title: Keto egg muffins
directions: Whisk the eggs together with seasoning and pesto. Add the cheese and stir.
Place the batter in muffin forms and add bacon, chorizo or salami.
Bake for 15–20 minutes, depending on the size of the muffin forms.
ingredients: 5 oz. 150 g air-dried chorizo or salami or cooked bacon
1 tablespoon red pesto or green pesto (optional)
